title: Catching Frogs
description: There's the old saying that you have to kiss a lot of frogs to find your prince. And for twenty five year old Marnie Cummings, that adage has rung true. She has kissed many, and is currently dating Liam Angstr√∂m, a tall, blonde, hot Swede investment banker. But still, she isn't feeling "it", whatever it may be. Then Marnie meets Lauren, her best friend Kendra's future sister in law. Feelings stir inside of her that she has never experienced, and Marnie wonders....Maybe it wasn't her prince she was searching for this whole time?TBR April 2013
author: Tania Penn
